com.epimorphics.jsonrdf.JSONWriterFacade

  • Packages that use JSONWriterFacade 
    Package Description
    com.epimorphics.jsonrdf
    The jsonrdf package provides serialisation of RDF models into JSON.
    com.epimorphics.jsonrdf.impl
    The impl package contains the default (and only) Encoder implementation.
